official_title: To award a congressional gold medal to Dr. Norman E. Borlaug.
short_title: Congressional Tribute to Dr. Norman E. Borlaug Act of 2006

summary.text: Congressional Tribute to Dr. Norman E. Borlaug Act of 2006 - Authorizes The President Pro Tempore of the Senate and the Speaker of the House of Representatives to make appropriate arrangements for the presentation, on behalf of Congress, of a gold medal of appropriate design, to Dr. Norman E. Borlaug, in recognition of his enduring contributions to the United States and the world.
